   Pantex Plant

   The Pantex Plant is America's only nuclear weapons assembly and
   disassembly facility.
   Located on the High Plains of the Texas Panhandle, 17 miles northeast
   of Amarillo, Pantex is centered on a 16,000-acre site just north of
   U.S. highway 60 in Carson City   Pantex Plant (Amarillo, TX)
